First, do not wait for motivation.

168
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:46,545
Action creates motivation, not the other way around.

169
00:08:46,545 --> 00:08:49,181
Second, make the task smaller.

170
00:08:49,181 --> 00:08:51,818
Ask TeraAI to break it down until it feels easy.

171
00:08:51,818 --> 00:08:54,454
Third, start with five minutes.

172
