Set a timer.

173
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:59,727
Read one explanation.

174
00:08:59,727 --> 00:09:02,363
Write three bullet points.

175
00:09:02,363 --> 00:09:04,999
Fourth, test yourself immediately.

176
00:09:04,999 --> 00:09:07,636
Ask TeraAI to quiz you.

177
00:09:07,636 --> 00:09:10,272
Make it active.

178
00:09:10,272 --> 00:09:12,909
And if it is still too hard, ask TeraAI to make it even smaller.

179
00:09:12,909 --> 00:09:15,545
Keep shrinking until you can start.

180
00:09:15,545 --> 00:09:18,181
You are not broken because you struggle to start studying.

181
00:09:18,181 --> 00:09:20,818
You may just need a smaller first step.

182
00:09:20,818 --> 00:09:23,454
And that is something AI can help with.

183
